              4242
              %span>
              4242
              %span>
              4242
          %tr
            %td
              %a{:href => "https://stripe.com/guides/strong-customer-authentication", :target => "_blank"} 3D Secure auth
              required:
            %td.card-number
              4000
              %span>
              0000
              %span>
              0000
              %span>
              3063
        %p.note
          See the
          %a{:href => "https://stripe.com/docs/testing#cards", :target => "_blank"} docs
          for a full list of test cards.
